<p>I can't think of a situation in which one would put the <a href="https://apple.stackexchange.com/questions/tagged/ibook" class="post-tag" title="show questions tagged &#39;ibook&#39;" rel="tag">ibook</a> tag to signify a question about a specific e-book.</p>
